OL,4,Cmove into double-decker buses
OL,6,FAntoni Taylor told ITV News' Kathy
OL,7,FWardle he'd put all of his savings
OL,8,Finto the project.
OL,10,FA family of eight from Cornwall who
OL,11,Fwere facing homelessness have turned
OL,12,Ftwo buses into emergency accommodation.
OL,14,FAntoni and Emma Taylor live with their
OL,15,Ffive children and Antoni's sister
OL,16,FHannah, who has cerebral palsy.
OL,18,FThe couple bought a coach believed to
OL,19,Fhave been used as a tour bus by
OL,20,FColdplay, and a former Newquay school
OL,21,Fbus to turn into their temporary home.
