OL,6,FThe family had been renting a cottage
OL,7,Fon the Lizard peninsula, but received
OL,8,Fa no-fault eviction notice from their
OL,9,Flandlord who needed to sell the
OL,10,Fproperty due to illness.
OL,12,FAntoni had planned to use savings to
OL,13,Fbuild an accessible property on a plot
OL,14,Fof land, but he claims delays in the
OL,15,Fplanning process have put paid to that
OL,16,Fdream.
OL,18,FAntoni told ITV News: "All of the
OL,19,Fmoney I had saved to start putting up
OL,20,Fa timber-framed house is all gone,
OL,21,Fbecause I've had to do something else.
