OL,6,F"My landlord needed me to leave and
OL,7,Fthat's not his fault. I tried a
OL,8,Fsolution, but I've been waiting nearly
OL,9,F18 months in the planning system."
OL,11,FAntoni says the family searched for
OL,12,Falternate accommodation in the private
OL,13,Frental sector as well as social
OL,14,Fhousing, but couldn't find anything
OL,15,Fthat would accommodate their family
OL,16,Fand Hannah's care needs.JHe said: "I
OL,17,Fdidn't want to end up in a situation
OL,18,Fwhere I was at the council's reception
OL,19,Fdesk with me my sister and our stuff
OL,20,Fsaying help us, which is what a lot of
OL,21,Fpeople are having to do down here.
