OL,6,F"Everything is too expensive, there's
OL,7,Fnothing to rent, they keep building
OL,8,Fthese massive executive homes that
OL,9,Fcost half a million pounds. Your
OL,10,Faverage teacher, nurse, firefighter,
OL,11,Fgrocery worker - no one can afford
OL,12,Fthat."JIn response, Cornwall Council
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are very sympathetic to
OL,14,Fthose who are finding it difficult to
OL,15,Ffind somewhere settled to live as
OL,16,FCornwall continues to experience
OL,17,Fextreme and unprecedented pressures on
OL,18,Fhousing.
