OL,6,F"There is a high demand for
OL,7,Faccommodation which includes our own
OL,8,Fhousing stock, properties that we
OL,9,Frent, or other accommodation.
OL,11,F"We're building more council housing
OL,12,Fand have bought open market homes to
OL,13,Fconvert into affordable housing for
OL,14,Flocal people in need.
OL,16,F"We're also working with developers,
OL,17,Flocal communities, and partners to
OL,18,Fidentify suitable sites."
