OL,6,FThe authority confirmed the family's
OL,7,Flatest planning application submitted
OL,8,Fin July 2023 has not yet been
OL,9,Fdetermined. It told ITV News it is
OL,10,Fcarefully considering the application,
OL,11,Fand intends to make a recommendation
OL,12,Fshortly.
OL,14,FAntoni says even if the application
OL,15,Fwas approved, he would now struggle to
OL,16,Fafford the build.
OL,18,FThe family is preparing to move into
OL,19,Fthe two buses and will be transporting
OL,20,Fthem to a new rented site by May this
OL,21,Fyear.
